page.title: 17GRID SQUARE CONTINUED
page.content: 9336:principle features include 1 nursery, 1 pumping station,the house called Farthings.The average height of the land is 225m above sea level. 9438:principle features include Fulford Dale Farm,Bakers Cottage,disused quarry ,sports ground,pumping station.The average height is 230m. 9437:the principle features include Stallington Heath,Cross Gate,Spot Acre spinney,Spot Acre,Mossgate and Broom's Farm.The average Height of the land is 234m. 9436:the principle features include the B5066 road,public house,Flats,Balaam's Lane,The spot (mixed woodland),Spot Farm and a mile post. 9538:principle features include a church with a tower,Fulford Hall,The Vicarage and part of the town of Fulford.
